**Overall Meaning:**

"I will explain the applications (or uses) of breath control, O virtuous one.  (One can practice it) at twilight, at dawn, at midday, or even always."

**Note:** This verse is introducing the discussion of when and how to practice pranayama, emphasizing its flexibility and the possibility of practicing it regularly throughout the day. 
